    "The GCN is illustrated in Fig. 2.",
    "As shown, the essence of the GCN lies in aggregating the features of neighboring nodes.",
    "By leveraging the relationships between nodes, GCN enable graph learning, which can be used for tasks such as node classification and graph classification",
    "In this paper, we propose a method for building an elevator fault diagnosis system based on digital twin PINNse-RGCN.",
    "Ns-e-RGCN represents two interconnected network models."
